channel.title: Java crashes when goin on HD(508+)
channel.description:
Hey, I used to be able to get on HD with rsps but since I haven't played RSPS in a long time I was going to play 1 again. And when I tried to switch to HD or tried to play a 508 which was HD only this happend: [URL=http://img836.imageshack.us/i/knipselm.png/][IMG]http://img836.imageshack.us/img836/4152/knipselm.png[/img][/URL]
English translation: Java(TM) Platform SE binary has stopped working (Rest isn't important)
Also normal Runescape is working fine (in hd) My PC specs:Windows 7 home premium, 32bit,4gb ram, Nvidia 9500 GT
extra info: My java is up to date and so is my graphics card
